node.accessibility_caption: An assortment of three in-games photo from Assassin’s Creed Valhalla by @minna.vp. An in-game photo of Assassin’s Creed Valhalla by @minna.vp. It shows a lone rowboat amidst a small lake. An overcast sky casts a somber light throughout the landscape, turning the trees that dot the plain into blueish silhouettes. The scant light from the sun reflects of the mostly calm waters.

An in-game photo of Assassin’s Creed Valhalla by @minna.vp. It shows a snowy hillside landscape at sunset, with the sun peeking through the treetops in the distance in a pink sky. Small brush and large rocks just out of the otherwise unblemished, blue-tinted snow.

An in-game photo of Assassin’s Creed Valhalla by @minna.vp. It shows the mythical land of Asgard, surrounded by dark waters and a purple fog. The various towers and spires reach up into the sky, covering the lower coast in shadow. In the sky beyond the World Tree, Yggdrasil looms over the landscape.
